    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015100/extras/69472511bd50f27b9aca51b04d2680b9.poster.avif?t=1722268488\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015100/extras/69472511bd50f27b9aca51b04d2680b9.webm?t=1722268488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015100/extras/69472511bd50f27b9aca51b04d2680b9.mp4?t=1722268488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>末日猫</strong>是一款氛围浓厚的硬核平台游戏，讲述了一只小黑猫穿越一个充满毒性和荒凉的后末日世界的故事，这个世界没有任何生命。玩家的目标是引导猫向上走向天堂，穿过毒云、危险的尖刺和石头障碍，以实现猫在燃烧的大地上度过的时间后的最终唯一梦想——到达一个宏伟的天堂。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015100/extras/47691e85bc1dfab7b9fc129db0092960.poster.avif?t=1722268488\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015100/extras/47691e85bc1dfab7b9fc129db0092960.webm?t=1722268488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015100/extras/47691e85bc1dfab7b9fc129db0092960.mp4?t=1722268488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2></strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >氛围体验：</h2></strong>沉浸在一个令人难以忘怀的美丽后末日环境中，令人惊叹的视觉效果和引人入胜的音轨增强了空旷和希望的感觉。<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挑战性的游戏玩法：</h2></strong>参与硬核平台游戏，具有精确的控制，每次跳跃和移动都必须精确计时，以避免致命的障碍并到达更高的地面。<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >引人入胜的故事情节：</h2></strong>跟随小黑猫感人的叙述，它唯一的愿望就是逃离破碎的世界，在天堂找到和平，为游戏玩法增添情感深度。<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的关卡设计：</h2></strong>在创意设计的关卡中导航，这些关卡具有毒云、尖锐的尖刺和危险的石头障碍，每个关卡都呈现出独特的挑战，考验你的平台技巧和战略思维。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul></ul>",
